<H3> <TI>   Radio Previews Visit by Bulgarian Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Radio Previews Visit by Bulgarian Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1905153294 Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network in 
Kyrgyz 2300 GMT 18 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1905153294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bishkek Kyrgyz Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Kyrgyz </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A delegation from Bulgaria led by Kadir Kadir, 
deputy chairman of the National Assembly, arrives on a one day 
working visit in Bishkek tomorrow. During the visit the 
Bulgarian delegation is scheduled to meet with members of the 
Kyrgyz Government and the Foreign Ministry and discuss the 
development of Kyrgyz-Bulgarian relations and the strengthening 
of ties between the two countries. 
  At the government building a ceremony to hand over a 
consignment of humanitarian aid brought from Bulgaria for the 
population of the areas which suffered from the natural calamity 
will take place. 

</TEXT>

