<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russian Border Guards Kill 20 Opposition Gunmen </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Border Guards Kill 20 Opposition Gunmen </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2005085094 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0800 GMT 
20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2005085094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Over the course of five days, Russian border guards 
carried out an operation to destroy gunmen in the rear sectors 
of the 11th and 12th posts of the Moskovskiy border guard 
detachment in Tajikistan. Since the beginning of May, gunmen 
have fired almost daily on details and military cantonments of 
the Russian border troops. According to preliminary 
information, which INTERFAX obtained from the press office of 
the Russian border troops, more than 20 gunmen of the Tajik 
opposition were killed and a large quantity of weapons and 
ammunition was seized during the operation. 

</TEXT>

