<H3> <TI>   Delegation Impressed With Chinese Reforms </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Delegation Impressed With Chinese Reforms </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1905094094 Moscow RIA in English 0818 GMT 19 May 94--FOR 
