<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Issues Edict on Social Policy Council </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Issues Edict on Social Policy Council </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1905194894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1627 GMT 19 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1905194894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] </F>
  [Text] Moscow May 19 TASS -- Taking into account the 
acuteness and significance of problems of a social policy, 
Russian President Boris Yeltsin issued a decree on the 
establishment of a council on a social policy attached to the 
president of the Russian Federation. 
  The primary tasks of the council will be to inform the head 
of state of the processes going on in the social sphere, working 
out proposals on a strategy of a social policy and its priority 
directions, the analysis and expertise of drafts of legislative 
acts on social issues, and the preparation of proposals on the 
conclusion of inter-state agreements and treaties on social 
issues. 
  Ella Panfilova was appointed chairman of the council. This 
was reported by the Russian president's press service. 

</TEXT>

