<H3> <TI>   `Tsentr' TV Company To Start Broadcasting 21 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Tsentr' TV Company To Start Broadcasting 21 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2005083094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0530 GMT 
20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2005083094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The "Tsentr" TV company starts broadcasting early on 
Saturday morning [May 21] on Ostankino's First Channel. This is 
the so called channel for late night viewers. It will start 
operating at 0145 hours [0945 GMT]. In the first broadcast you 
can watch the French film "The Snatch Squad." In the long-term, 
the organizers are planning various entertaining topics, 
together with reportage on the life of nocturnal Moscow. 

