<H3> <TI>   Tu-160 Bomber Production Halted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tu-160 Bomber Production Halted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2005081594 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1325 GMT 17 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PM2005081594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "M-Trust" program: Announcer-read report over </F>
video of Tu-160] 
  [Text] The Kazan Aviation Association named for Gorbunov 
has halted production of the Tu-160 strategic missile carriers, 
the POSTFAKTUM AERO Agency reports. 
  Each such plane costs several billion rubles. The last few 
to have been produced are yet to be claimed and paid for by the 
Army. They remain at the plant. 

</TEXT>

