<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Colonel General Vladimir Semenov, commander in chief 
of the Russian ground forces, has said that the attempts of 
Russian President Boris Yeltsin and Defense Minister Pavel 
Grachev to resolve the issue of the Black Sea Fleet have not 
yielded any tangible results so far because of the nationalist 
ambitions of the Ukrainian leadership. Semenov spoke today at a 
briefing in Moscow, RIA reported. 

</TEXT>

