<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Seeks Early Solution of Black Sea Fleet Issue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kravchuk Seeks Early Solution of Black Sea Fleet Issue </PHRASE></F></HT>

