  [Text] We will begin with a statement by the Ukrainian 
Defense Ministry Press Service. 
  The world public has again been misled, reads the statement. 
Again referring to a "source close to the Black Sea Fleet 
headquarters," I read the original, ITAR-TASS circulated 
misinformation on 19 May as if 1,000 special purpose troops from 
the Ukrainian armed forces have arrived on the territory of 
Crimea over the last 24 hours. The same "source" reported the 
concentration of 300 Ukrainian servicemen in the vicinity of 
Sevastopol. 
