<H3> <TI>   Government Approves Regulations on State Border </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Approves Regulations on State Border </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2005093994 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 2155 GMT 19 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2005093994 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAR </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Kiev, 19 May -- The Ukrainian Cabinet of Ministers 
has approved a resolution on the creation of a border strip. It 
is being established along Ukraine's state border in areas of 
land, along the shores of frontier rivers, and within 
settlements and rural councils of people's deputies adjacent to 
the border. 
  The border regime regulations were also confirmed. 

</TEXT>

