<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   LDPR Boycotts Duma Session in Protests of `Lies' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    LDPR Boycotts Duma Session in Protests of `Lies' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2005171594 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel 
