<H3> <TI>   No Plans To Sack Yerin </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    No Plans To Sack Yerin </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2005184294 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1639 GMT 20 May 94 </F>
