  [Text] Odessa, 20 May -- "The aggressive aspirations of the 
imperial-military Kiev, which is striving to trample down 
Crimea's sovereignty, deserve resolute condemnation. Yuriy 
Meshkov will not be right if he yields to blackmail and agrees 
to compromises," this is how Lev Vershynin, the cochairman of 
