<H3> <TI>   Talks Agreed Between Ukraine, Crimea on Settling Situation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talks Agreed Between Ukraine, Crimea on Settling Situation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2205095294 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0930 
GMT 22 May 94 </F>

