<F P=106> [Report by UKRINFORM correspondent Lev Ryabchikov for TASS] </F>
  [Text] Simferopol, 22 May -- The Crimean-Ukrainian 
parliamentary talks on unblocking the situation on the peninsula 
following the adoption of the law on restoring the Crimean 
Constitution of 6 May 1992 will be held in the next few days. 
On Monday [23 May] or Tuesday Simferopol and Kiev will hold 
